message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.BIO, cs.NEURON - The paper presents a deep learning pipeline for analysing placenta histology at the level of the cell, which involves image analysis and classification. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the potential for this pipeline to improve our understanding of basic cellular placental biology and its variations, which could be relevant to the bioinformatics (cs.BIO) and neuroscience (cs.NEURON) sub-categories.
